                        ana="http://syriaca.org/keyword/persecution http://syriaca.org/keyword/travel http://syriaca.org/keyword/exile http://syriaca.org/keyword/suffering http://syriaca.org/keyword/monasticism">
                        <desc> 
                            For a third time,<persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/3719"> the community</persName>was forced to leave
